<p>Here's an attempt at curating the ambassador series list, with an aim of including stuff that is some combination of influential, good, introductory or different genres. I will list it in descending order of fit, with, I think the more obvious choices near the top and ones that I am less certain about later.</p>
<ol>
<li><em>Orientation</em></li>
<li><em>A Cool War</em></li>
<li><em>The Lombardi Tales</em></li>
<li><em>Learning the Alphabet</em></li>
<li><em>There is No Antimemetics Division</em></li>
<li><em>Harper</em></li>
<li><em>Peregrine</em></li>
<li><em>Dixieland Nightmare Magic</em></li>
<li><em>First Suite</em></li>
<li><em>Apotheosis</em></li>
</ol>

