			<div class="content" id="post-content-3901025">
									

<p>Not a bad selection, but if we're going to do format-screws, I'd rather us stick with mainlist SCPs; so, no 001s or -Js.</p>
<p>I would suggest the 001 be replaced by &quot;The Minotaur'sTale&quot;. The -J will need to be replaced.</p>
<p>Finally, I <em>think</em> I specify on the page (or maybe here in the comments?) that entries in active contests are not accepted. The selection should either be replaced, otherwise this proposal must wait until after the contest closes to be implemented on this page.</p>

