<p>Aaaaaaaaalirghty folks! We have ourselves a brand-spankin' new category!</p>
<p>&quot;Religion, Myths, Legends and Folklore&quot; brings us the best the wiki has to offer in gods &amp; demons, tricksters &amp; prometheans, legendary creatures and mythic races!</p>
<p>Big thanks to all the folks on the irc and scpdeclassified discords for helping to build this inaugural list of 75. It's a little short of the original plan of 100&#8230; but that's what Proposals are for! Be sure to read the How To Contribute on this page to see how to make suggestions!</p>

